title: DataLoader behave differently between 0.10 and 0.12
body_html:
When I'm doing imagenet classification evaluation in 0.10, classID is alphebatical, and evaluate order is the store order in my FS.

In 0.12 this behavior is changed when my code is kept the same.

Any ideas? I appreciate your help very much since I'm attending a Kaggle competition.
